{"id":"heled","term":"Heled","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>This world, (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:30\">1 Chr. 11:30</a>); called Heleb (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:29\">2 Sam. 23:29</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 11:30","2 Samuel 23:29"]}